_:Nc2eb832abd36423f82bd8f863dfd9201 <http://schema.org/description> "Consumer Council for Water (CCW) represents water and sewerage consumers in England and Wales and takes up unresolved complaints. CCW is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Environment, Food & Rural Affairs ." .
